### Optimization: Request Fusion
# Batch similar requests together for cost savings
POST https://api.costkatana.com/api/optimizations/batch
CostKatana-Auth: Bearer YOUR_COSTKATANA_KEY
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requests": [
    {"prompt": "Translate 'hello' to Spanish"},
    {"prompt": "Translate 'goodbye' to Spanish"},
    {"prompt": "Translate 'thank you' to Spanish"}
  ],
  "service": "openai",
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "options": {
    "enableRequestFusion": true
  }
}

### Expected: 50-70% cost reduction by batching
